urst. We further investigate the high\nvelocity dispersion in the central region. We find that the ISM turbulent\npressure derived from the gas velocity dispersion is in equilibrium with the\nweight of the ISM. This argues against extra power from AGN feedback that\nsignificantly affects the kinematics of the cold molecular gas.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Feb 2023 11:36:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Feb 2023 02:20:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-05"}
